  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And the most important thing that we-- any one of us can do is to make sure that the younger generation, our generation, everybody's younger generation, understands how far a little bit of closing your eyes can lead to.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "If it doesn't happen to you, it's not as bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "It happens to all of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And if this happens, the world will not be a fit place to live in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So we must all be very, very, very careful to do everything that we can to make sure that this seed of hatred doesn't come to flower again, and destroys another generation.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I think that's what-- that what I would like-- if I would know what to do about it, that's what I would like my life's work to be.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But of course, I am totally powerless.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I want to live my own life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I have worked so hard like a dog, all my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I want to coast for the rest of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you for listening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a privilege to be allowed to tell it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
